data.description: THIS HOME IS USDA ELIGIBLE!! Welcome to your new home!! This ranch style home is located in the growing city of Simpsonville! This gem sits on a gorgeous .6 acre lot, one of the largest in the neighborhood! Enjoy peace and quiet tucked at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac! Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, this home offers ample space for your family! Enjoy the convenience of a Ranch style home, with a layout designed for both comfort and functionality! This highly desirable location ensures you’ll have easy access to the best that Simpsonville has to offer! Don’t miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your new home sweet home!!
